name: Catinga
description:
My first single ever released goes crypto!

"A berimbau drubbing. Catinga is that bad smell on living beings. This unconventional instrumental hip hop paints an urban landscape reflected in the eyes of the human animal as a manifest against the post-truth.
The mixture of the processed berimbau samples with electronic keys consolidates the aesthetics of the composer and producer felino. The chaotic rhythm was inspired by the maracatu, a Northeastern Brazil´s music" Brasil, 2020.

music production: felino
